name: Low-Chroma Squiggles #42210
description:
This series uses the same core algorithm as the t-SNE series [1] but uses different parameter settings and color palettes. The color palettes were inspired by a post about using low-chroma colors [2]. Created on Nov. 6, 2021. Made in R using the {ggplot2} and {Rtsne} packages.

Sources:
[1] https://clauswilke.com/art/project/t-sne
[2] https://clauswilke.com/art/post/colors-reduce-chroma
